caller_intent: Bobby Jenkins wants to understand the new insurance premiums after his policy was changed with Travelers and clarify how payments will work.
resolution_steps: Agent confirmed the policy change with Travelers effective November 25th for $1,641.
Agent explained Travelers should send payment notices but acknowledged none had been received yet.
Agent offered to check Travelers' system directly for precise premium details and payment schedules.
Agent requested Bobby's phone number (413-1326) to call back with the information.
summary: Bobby Jenkins contacted Alliance Insurance to inquire about new Travelers policy premiums after a recent change. The agent confirmed the policy details and offered to check Travelers' system directly for precise payment information, scheduling a callback to provide full details.
